---
// Sticky magazine chrome — logo mark (clipped-corner square, per the
// design system) + sparse top-right links. Shop/Contact aren't real
// destinations (this is a from-scratch recreation of an offline site),
// so they stay "#" like the original mockup; Articles points at the
// /serial index. The mobile burger is a static glyph, not wired to a
// menu — this is a portfolio piece, not a live product, and the nav
// links collapse away under 820px per the design system's own rule.
---

<header class="nav">
	<a class="logo" href="/serial">
		<span class="mk">S</span>
		<span class="nm">serial</span>
	</a>
	<nav class="links">
		<a href="#">Shop</a>
		<a href="/serial">Articles</a>
		<a href="#">Contact</a>
	</nav>
	<button class="burger" aria-label="menu">&#9776;</button>
</header>
